{"tid":345554,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[HeHe]йҰҷжёҜжёёжіійҒӢеӢ•е“ЎиҰӘеҜҶиЎҢзӮәжӣқе…үрҹ“ё","createTime":"2017-08-03T07:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T05:16:30.000Z","uid":2547,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1722ec07658f90fe0733383241e23103657b0c","tid":345554,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"пј»ж…Һе…ҘпјҪйҰҷжёҜйҒӢеӢ•е“Ўиў«жҖ§дҫөз…§жӣқе…үрҹ“ё<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/299850/page/12?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/299850/page/12?ref=ios</a><br />\nз№јдёҠдёҖеҖӢpostеҲҶдә«й—ңж–јжҺ’зҗғйҒӢеӢ•е“Ўж—ўиҰӘеҜҶиЎҢзӮә<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nе‘ўж¬Ўе°ұеҲҶдә«дёӢжёёжіійҒӢеӢ•е“Ўж—ўиҰӘеҜҶиЎҢзӮә<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/151322_43d9984b034ac998bfba2c6eeb4392c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F151322_43d9984b034ac998bfba2c6eeb4392c6.jpg&h=ee6060b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. йҡҠеҸӢAејөеӨ§еҳҙе·ҙе°Қи‘—йҡҠеҸӢBиӘӘпјҡгҖҢе””gur?жҗһжҲ‘дё«з¬Ё<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> гҖҚ<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/151545_cd862ce87bdb37d8f3b54603edd879a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F151545_cd862ce87bdb37d8f3b54603edd879a9.jpg&h=811e4e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/151549_280052497efe1a0a1195d34891abdd5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F151549_280052497efe1a0a1195d34891abdd5d.jpg&h=8dcf2672&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/151552_768ad390c1316896794c90ff31502ad6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F151552_768ad390c1316896794c90ff31502ad6.jpg&h=1367dfd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. йҡҠеҸӢBиҒҪзҪ·дҫҝдәҢи©ұдёҚиӘӘз«ӢеҚідјёеҮәеҸіжүӢжҸёдәҶйҡҠеҸӢAйӣ„еҺҡзҡ„иғёиӮҢдёҖдёӢ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/152026_a57792488b3f0a0409b2e17c8e453c1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F152026_a57792488b3f0a0409b2e17c8e453c1d.jpg&h=b829a6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. з”ұж–јйҡҠеҸӢBжҸёиғёзҡ„еҠӣйҒ“еӨӘеӨ§ йҡҠеҸӢAйңІеҮәе«ҢжЈ„зҡ„иЎЁжғ… з”ҹдәҶйҡҠеҸӢBзҡ„ж°Ј<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/153130_86ec0e1314478496cbe5d06dbd3b8425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F153130_86ec0e1314478496cbe5d06dbd3b8425.jpg&h=efc3c4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. йҡЁеҫҢе…©дәәдёҖеҗҢжҙ—жҫЎ еӨ§е®¶дёҖеҗҢеҫ®з¬‘еҗҲз…§ йӣҷж–№й—ңдҝӮеҸҲеҶҚе’ҢеҘҪеҰӮеҲқ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">еҗҢе ҙеҠ еҪұжёёжіійҒӢеӢ•е“Ўд№Ӣж—ҘеёёзҶұиә«е§ҝеӢў<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/153302_c2194fd717489212e8fd641efddfafab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F153302_c2194fd717489212e8fd641efddfafab.jpg&h=30b1caab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f75fc44065faeb1df5308afcedf846191e25ad4","tid":345554,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"еҳ©жңҖе°ҫе—°ејө еҘҪжңүжҪӣеҠӣеҒҡ0д»”<im